name: Oncology Scientific Update in Covid Pandemic
content: International Association of Oncology (IAO) one of the leading professional associations for medical oncology & life science professionals caring for people meant for research and development in the field of medical oncology and life science is organizing a free webinar on “Oncology Scientific Update in Covid Pandemic” on 18th July, 2020 at 5.00 PM to 6.00 PM
